<A>__{we pull back to reveal we're looking at the sun. in the distance lie the gorgeous san gabriel mountains and the downtown los angeles skyline. in one long tracking shot, we crane past some trees to reveal the vast expansive homes scattered in the hills of brentwood. homeowners walk dogs, a paperboy chucks papers from a gleaming mountain bike... it's early in the morning, and the landscapers haven't come with their leaf blowers yet. continue booming down to road level to face the resplendent martin residence. we steadicam down the front walk, able to admire the manicured hedges and the black escalade in the driveway, to the front door decorated with a whimsical placard that reads, "the martins" and we pass through the keyhole into the foyer.}
